From: Jiang Lu <lu.jiang@windriver.com>
Date: Tue, 22 Jul 2014 15:36:51 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Netlogic: update load address when closed MAPPED kernel

Forcing load address to 0xffffffff81000000 for kernel closed CONFIG_MAPPED
for netlogic platform.

Signed-off-by: Jiang Lu <lu.jiang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/mips/netlogic/Platform |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/mips/netlogic/Platform b/arch/mips/netlogic/Platform
index 8b893ab..1f73d09 100644
--- a/arch/mips/netlogic/Platform
+++ b/arch/mips/netlogic/Platform
@@ -18,5 +18,5 @@ platform-$(CONFIG_NLM_COMMON)  	+= netlogic/
 ifdef CONFIG_MAPPED_KERNEL
 load-$(CONFIG_NLM_COMMON)  	+= 0xffffffffc0100000
 else
-load-$(CONFIG_NLM_COMMON)  	+= 0xffffffff80100000
+load-$(CONFIG_NLM_COMMON)  	+= 0xffffffff81000000
 endif
